entity-family-tables-viewport-misc — TABLE, VIEWPORT, and misc graphical
========================================================================

Status: DEFERRED (schms-parity 1.6.6). Parent: entity-mutation-parity.

Not yet in the entity-family registry (accepted permissively):

  - ACAD_TABLE / TABLE (+ TABLESTYLE object) — a block-reference-derived
    grid; cells, row/column geometry.
  - VIEWPORT — the paper-space viewport entity (68/69 status/id,
    the frozen-layer 331 list, 90 flags). ENTMOD on VIEWPORT is
    documented as unsupported (spec ENTMOD note) — model that.
  - SHAPE (AcDbShape: 2 name, 39 thickness, 40 size).
  - LIGHT / SUN / GEOPOSITIONMARKER / SECTIONOBJECT / CAMERA.
  - ATTDEF/ATTRIB advanced (the MTEXT-attribute 71/72/74 alignment and
    the multiline-attribute 340/70 codes; the base families ARE
    registered with the minimal required set).

Do
--

Register descriptors + dependent style/object records, honour the
VIEWPORT ENTMOD restriction, add tests.

Reference: AutoCAD DXF reference, ACAD_TABLE/VIEWPORT/SHAPE/LIGHT/SUN.
